B.a5a=new A.f("im_18",B.u,"Side-by-side full merge: Lying on sides facing each other: one leg slides between mine, the other hooks outside, interlocking like interlocking gears. Chests press flat first \u2014 nipples brushing, then flattening with weight. Stomachs mold; hips nestle tightly. The merge is total: from shoulders to ankles, bodies form one continuous plane. Figure-eight grinds begin at the hips \u2014 slow loops that ripple upward through torsos (ribs expanding together) and downward through legs (thighs flexing in sequence). Warmth pools where pubic bones meet, spreading like slow-moving honey; sweat gathers in the creases of bent knees and elbows. The motion creates a continuous, flowing friction \u2014 skin gliding with faint, wet whispers, breaths fanning cheeks in warm pulses.","assets/images/pos_im18.png","Side-by-side full merge: Sides par let jao face-to-face: ek leg mere legs ke beech slide hogi, dusri bahar, interlocking gears ki tarah. Chests flat press honge \u2014 nipples brushing, phir weight ke saath flat. Stomachs mold; hips nestle tightly. Merge total hai: shoulders se ankles tak, bodies ek continuous plane banayengi. Figure-eight grinds hips se shuru honge \u2014 slow loops jo torsos aur legs mein ripple karenge. Warmth pubic bones par pool karegi aur slow-moving honey ki tarah phail jayegi. Sweat knee aur elbows ke creases mein jama hoga. Motion continuous friction banayega \u2014 skin wet whispers ke saath glide karegi.")
